                <h2>1. Santorini, Greece: A Mediterranean Vacation for Couples on a Budget</h2>
                <p>Sail along those Sinquinese iconic sunsets, their brilliant white architecture, and sparkling sapphire-blue waters, which spell romance. And although it is best known as the place where the elite have their holiday, it doesn’t mean you cannot travel there on a budget.</p>
