                <h2>2. Ubud, Bali: Tranquillity in Tropical Paradise</h2>
                <p>Tucked in the very heart of Bali is Ubud, a couple’s hideaway when it comes to peace and romance. With its rice terraces and temples, tranquil and yet inexpensive luxury, Ubud is just perfect as a budget getaway. Enjoy cosy and pretty villas and boutique guest houses that offer comfort without high costs.</p>
